Albedo plot has made outliers

clim |> 
  pivot_longer(cols = c(SWin, SWout), names_to = "SW", values_to = "value") |> 
  ggplot() + 
  geom_path(aes(date_time, value, color = SW)) + 
  scale_color_brewer(palette = "Set1") + 
  ggtitle("LWVS Shortwave") + 
  theme_bw(base_size = 18)
